      "title": "[Boing Boing] A cheap blood pressure pill can take the sting out of painful memories",
      "content_html": "<img src=\"https://i0.wp.com/boingboing.net/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/propranolol.jpg?fit=1200%2C1200&quality=60&ssl=1\" style=\"width:100%;max-height:300px;object-fit:cover;\" />\n<a href=\"https://boingboing.net/2026/03/05/a-cheap-blood-pressure-pill-can-take-the-sting-out-of-painful-memories.html\" rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"A cheap blood pressure pill can take the sting out of painful memories\"><img alt=\"Propranolol (Wirestock Creators/shutterstock.com)\" class=\"webfeedsFeaturedVisual wp-post-image\" height=\"1200\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/boingboing.net/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/propranolol.jpg?fit=1200%2C1200&amp;quality=60&amp;ssl=1\" style=\"display: block; margin: auto; margin-bottom: 5px;\" width=\"1200\" /></a><p>Every time you recall a painful memory, your brain has to re-save it — and propranolol, a cheap beta-blocker commonly prescribed for blood pressure, interferes with that process. Take it before recalling a bad experience, and the memory comes back duller, less emotionally charged. &#8212; <a class=\"read-more\" href=\"https://boingboing.net/2026/03/05/a-cheap-blood-pressure-pill-can-take-the-sting-out-of-painful-memories.html\">Read the rest </a></p>\n<p>The post <a href=\"https://boingboing.net/2026/03/05/a-cheap-blood-pressure-pill-can-take-the-sting-out-of-painful-memories.html\">A cheap blood pressure pill can take the sting out of painful memories</a> appeared first on <a href=\"https://boingboing.net\">Boing Boing</a>.</p>",
      "date_published": "2026-03-05T22:59:06+00:00",
      "authors": [
